        <UserObject label="" mermaidData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;sequenceDiagram\n    participant U as Cliente\n    participant AS as AccountServiceImpl\n    participant CC as CustomerClient\n    participant CRC as CreditClient\n    participant Repo as AccountRepository\n    participant Red as Redis\n\n    U-&gt;&gt;AS: create(Account)\n    AS-&gt;&gt;CC: getCustomerById(customerId)\n    AS-&gt;&gt;CRC: hasOverdueDebt(customerId)\n    alt Tiene deuda o Cliente inválido\n        AS--&gt;&gt;U: 403/400 Error\n    else Cliente Válido\n        AS-&gt;&gt;AS: validateCustomerProfile(VIP/PYME)\n        alt Perfil inválido (ej. VIP sin Savings)\n            AS--&gt;&gt;U: 403 Forbidden\n        else Validación exitosa\n            AS-&gt;&gt;Repo: save(account)\n            AS-&gt;&gt;Red: set(\&quot;account:\&quot; + id, account)\n            AS--&gt;&gt;U: 201 Created\n        end\n    end&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;config&quot;: null&#xa;}" id="8KX7o14pzl8vngNsX80g-25">
